dc_title_s: Northumbria, Cumberlandia, et Dunelmensis Episcopatus; Amstelodami, sumptibus Henrici Hondij.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Title cartouche includes fruits and grape vines. From the Appendix Atlas of the British Isles and Northern Europe, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. Does not match any states listed in Van der Krogt. 1 map: 33 x 45 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Hondius, Hendrik, 1597-1651.,Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664. Appendix Atlas of the British Isles and Northern Europe.,Hondius, Hendrik, 1597-1651. Appendix Atlas of the British Isles and Northern Europe.,Vignaud, Henry, 1830-1922, former owner.
